# Tool-scan exclusions for oxfmt only (not VCS policy — see .gitignore).
# These paths contain Claude Code runtime files that surface as unreadable
# character-device nodes under this environment's sandboxing, which makes
# oxfmt fail with "Failed to read file" errors if it attempts to scan them.
.claude
.superpowers
.mcp.json

